data.title: Fish Tank
data.text:
Screenwriter: Andrea Arnold

Producer: Kees Kasander

MUBI x Vidiots present: A whole day of free coming-of-age classics! Join us Saturday, January 27, and watch hand-picked films (Tomboy, Fish Tank) which inspired Cannes-winning director Molly Manning Walker’s celebrated new film (How to Have Sex), and The Virgin Suicides, chosen by Vidiots!

Free entry, popcorn, and more fun from our friends at MUBI. Vidiots members can also stream the collection “Growing Pains: Coming-of-age Films” free on MUBI for 30 days with a special offer here.

Plus, see a special free sneak preview of How to Have Sex at Vidiots Tuesday, January 30 at 7:00pm, featuring a post-film conversation with director Molly Manning Walker. A MUBI Release.
